  "text": "3 [CITATION_1] , or security guards failing to see an unusual or suspicious individual on a security video feed (Nasholm et al., 2014) . Inattentional blindness can result in distracted drivers not seeing a child about to enter traffic [CITATION_2] , or an athlete not seeing an open teammate during a big game [CITATION_3] .",
